  "body": "After upgrading to besu `22.4.1`,\r\nI get following error\r\n```\r\nUnknown option: '--engine-rpc-http-port=8550'\r\nPossible solutions: --engine-rpc-enabled, --engine-rpc-port, --engine-jwt-secret, --engine-jwt-enabled, --engine-host-allowlist\r\n\r\nTo display full help:\r\nbesu [COMMAND] --help\r\nStream closed EOF for staking/besu-node-0 (besu-node)\r\n```\r\nNo breaking changes in the release notes mentioned about\r\n\r\nCan you add an alias for `--engine-rpc-http-port`?\r\nThanks",
